tItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527918\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527918\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gma1665702671256.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gma1665702671256.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gma1665702671256.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gma1665702671256\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Sets the default window properties of the application shell.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"gma1665702671256__topic_d144602e1_d144603e1_d144604e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gma1665702671256__p_d144605e1_d144606e1_d144607e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Shell</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ushell</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Properties</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gma1665702671256__section_g21_jsc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d284945e75\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Properties</var>—semi-colon delimited list of property-value pairs</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Application Shell Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">Physical Property Name</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\">Property</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">BackColor</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">Background color of the window.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">BackImage</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scc1665702611448.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scc1665702611448.html\" title=\"Image used as background for the application window, form, or entity. This property can be set in ProcScript.\">Background Image (BackImage)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">Background image of the window.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">HAlign</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kmv1665702611521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmv1665702611521.html\" title=\"This property determines how the data (text or image) is aligned in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Horizontal Alignment (Halign)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">Horizontal alignment of the background image.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">VAlign</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gvp1665702611605.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gvp1665702611605.html\" title=\"This property determines the vertical alignment of data (text or image) in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Vertical Alignment ( Valign)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">Horizontal scaling of the background image</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">Hscale</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbd1665702611680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbd1665702611680.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is horizontally scaled; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">Vertical alignment of background image.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">VScale</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sup1665702611757.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sup1665702611757.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is scaled vertically; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Vertical Scaling ( Vscale)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">Vertical scaling of background image.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">PreserveAspect</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yxe1665702611833.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxe1665702611833.html\" title=\"Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False.\">Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">Specify whether to preserve the aspect ratio of the background image at all\n                times.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">MessageLine</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wjh1665702607394.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wjh1665702607394.html\" title=\"The MessageLine property determines whether the message line is displayed at the bottom of the application window. This is used to display non-obtrusive messages to the user.\">Message Line</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">Show or hide the message line at the bottom of the application window.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">state</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xwv1665702674089.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xwv1665702674089.html\" title=\"This section of the initialization file records the state of certain UPI objects when the user exits an application.\">[state]</a></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">The application shell window state.<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gma1665702671256__ul_z15_j33_nvb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">NORMAL</code> (default)</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">MAXIMIZED</code></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">MINIMIZED</code></li>\n</ul></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">XPosPerc</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\"> </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">The horizontal application shell window position, as a percentage relative to\n                the relative to the primary Windows desktop.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">YPosPerc</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\"> </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">The vertical window position, as a percentage relative to the relative to the\n                primary Windows desktop.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">XSizePerc</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\"> </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">The horizontal window size, as a percentage as a percentage relative to the\n                relative to the primary Windows desktop.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">YSizePerc</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\"> </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">The vertical window size, as a percentage relative to the relative to the\n                primary Windows desktop.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__1\">Layouthistory</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__2\"> </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"gma1665702671256__table_r15_j33_nvb__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">TRUE ( default) | FALSE</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Save or load the size and position of the application shell to or from the\n                  Windows Registry. Positions from the history are ignored when the position is\n                  defined in the property string.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gma1665702671256__table_d17564e1_d17565e1_d17566e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ila1665702671184.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ila1665702671184.html\" title=\"The [application] section of the initialization file enables you to set application-level defaults for a Windows desktop application.\">[application]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gma1665702671256__section_x3v_5sc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d284945e430\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Default properties defined here can be overridden by application shell definitions and the\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$applproperties</span> ProcScript function. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifq1665702843454.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifq1665702843454.html\" title=\"Set the presentation properties of the application shell.\">$applproperties</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gma1665702671256__section_fpd_yjv_cdc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d284945e449\">Example: Setting Shell Properties </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Setting the background color and image, and the alignment and scaling properties of the\n        background image:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"gma1665702671256__pre_dhr_yjv_cdc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[application]\nshell = ushell (backimage=@largeLogo.jpg;valign=top;halign=left;hscale=80;vscale=80; backcolor=ivory)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifq1665702843454.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$applproperties</a><p>Set the presentation properties of the application shell.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527918\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527918\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Shell Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Sets the default window properties of the application shell. Shell = ushell ( Properties ) Arguments Properties —semi-colon delimited list of property-value pairs Table 1. Application Shell Properties Physical Property Name Property Description BackColor Background Color (BackColor) Background color of the window. BackImage Background Image (BackImage) Background image of the window. HAlign Horizontal Alignment (Halign) Horizontal alignment of the background image. VAlign Vertical Alignment ( Valign) Horizontal scaling of the background image Hscale Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale) Vertical alignment of background image. VScale Vertical Scaling ( Vscale) Vertical scaling of background image. PreserveAspect Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect) Specify whether to preserve the aspect ratio of the background image at all times. MessageLine Message Line Show or hide the message line at the bottom of the application window. state [state] The application shell window state. NORMAL (default) MAXIMIZED MINIMIZED XPosPerc The horizontal application shell window position, as a percentage relative to the relative to the primary Windows desktop. YPosPerc The vertical window position, as a percentage relative to the relative to the primary Windows desktop. XSizePerc The horizontal window size, as a percentage as a percentage relative to the relative to the primary Windows desktop. YSizePerc The vertical window size, as a percentage relative to the relative to the primary Windows desktop. Layouthistory TRUE ( default) | FALSE Save or load the size and position of the application shell to or from the Windows Registry. Positions from the history are ignored when the position is defined in the property string. Default value: None File section: [application] Description Default properties defined here can be overridden by application shell definitions and the $applproperties ProcScript function. For more information, see $applproperties . Example: Setting Shell Properties Setting the background color and image, and the alignment and scaling properties of the background image: [application] shell = ushell (backimage=@largeLogo.jpg;valign=top;halign=left;hscale=80;vscale=80; backcolor=ivory) Copy Related Links $applproperties Set the presentation properties of the application shell. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}